quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  28,51,"wlqd fssalna wbyana alquran rahmatan bqwmk 'ayuha alrswl; laealahum ytdhkrwn, fytezu bh"
  28,52,aldhyn ataynahum alkitab min qabl alquran -whm alyhwd walnsara aldhyn lm ybddilu- yuminun bialquran wbmhmd ealayh alsalat walslam
  28,53,"w'idha ytla hdha alquran ealaa aladhin ataynahum alktab, qalu: sddaqna bh, wemlna bima fyh, 'iinah alhaqu min eind rbna, 'iinaa kunaa min qabl nzwlh muslimin mwhdyn, fdyn allah wahd, wahu al'islam"
  28,54,"hwla' aladhin tqddamat sftuhm yutawn thawab eamalahum mrtyn: ealaa al'iiman bktabhm, waealaa 'iimanuhum bialquran bima sbru, wamin awsafhm 'anahum yadfaeun alsayiyat balhsnt, wamimaa razaqnahum yunfiqun fi sabil alkhayr walbr. wa'iidha sumie hwla' alqawm albatil min alqawl lm yusghu 'ilyh, wqalu: lana 'aemaluna la nhyd enha, walakum 'aemalukum wwzrha elykm, fnhn la nshghl 'anfusina bialradi elykm, wala tasmaeun mnna 'iilaa alkhyr, wala nkhatbhm bmqtda jhlkm; li'anana la nurid tariq aljahilin wala nhbha. whdha min khayr ma yaquluh aldeat 'iilaa allh"
  28,55,"hwla' aladhin tqddamat sftuhm yutawn thawab eamalahum mrtyn: ealaa al'iiman bktabhm, waealaa 'iimanuhum bialquran bima sbru, wamin awsafhm 'anahum yadfaeun alsayiyat balhsnt, wamimaa razaqnahum yunfiqun fi sabil alkhayr walbr. wa'iidha sumie hwla' alqawm albatil min alqawl lm yusghu 'ilyh, wqalu: lana 'aemaluna la nhyd enha, walakum 'aemalukum wwzrha elykm, fnhn la nshghl 'anfusina bialradi elykm, wala tasmaeun mnna 'iilaa alkhyr, wala nkhatbhm bmqtda jhlkm; li'anana la nurid tariq aljahilin wala nhbha. whdha min khayr ma yaquluh aldeat 'iilaa allh"
  28,56,"'ink -ayha alrswl- la tahdi hdayt tawfiq man 'ahbabt hdayth, wlkn dhlk biad allah yahdi man yasha' 'an yahdiah ll'iyman, wayuafiquh 'ilyh, wahu 'aelam biman yuslih llhdayt fyhdyh"
  28,57,"wqal kafaar \"mk\": 'iin natabie alhaqi aladhi jitana bh, wntbra min alawlya' walalht, nutakhattaf min 'ardina balqtl walasr wnhb alamwal, 'awalam najealahum mtmknyn fi balad amn, hrramna ealaa alnaas safk aldima' fyh, yujlb 'iilayh thamarat kuli shay' rzqana min ldna? wlkn 'akthar hwla' almushrikin la yaelamun qadr hadhih alnaeam elyhm, fyshkru man 'aneam ealayhim biha wytyewh"
  28,58,"wkthyr min 'ahl alquraa 'ahlaknahum hin 'alhathm maeishatahum ean al'iiman balrsl, fakafaruu wtghawa, fatilk masakinuhum lam tuskn min baedihim 'iilaa qalilana mnha, wakunaa nahn alwarithin lileibad nmythm, thuma yurjaeun 'ilyna, fnjazyhm baemalhm"
  28,59,"wma kan rabuk -ayha alrswl- muhlik alquraa alati hawl \"mk\" fi zmank hataa yabeath fi 'umiha -why \"mk\"- rasulana yatlu ealayhim ayatna, wama kunaa muhliki alquraa 'iilaa wa'ahluha zalimun lanfshm bikufrihim biallah wmesyth, fahum bdhlk msthqwn lleqwbt walnkal"